<main>
    <section class="content">
        <h2>Input & Output Devices</h2>

        <img src="/img/devices.png" alt="Computer Input and Output Devices">

        <p>
            Input and output devices allow people to interact with a computer.
            Input devices send information to the computer, while output devices
            present information back to the user.
        </p>

        <p>
            Without these devices, it would be impossible to enter commands,
            view results, hear audio, or print documents. They make computers
            useful for everyday tasks.
        </p>

        <h3>Common Examples</h3>

        <ul>
            <li>Keyboard</li>
            <li>Mouse</li>
            <li>Monitor</li>
            <li>Printer</li>
            <li>Speakers</li>
            <li>Microphone</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</main>

